description:
this is highly compressed version of god of war 1 for pc using pcsx2 emulator..

Step no:01
firstly go to god of war\PCSX2-r2711_0.9.6_and_0.9.7_and_Plugins\0.9.6&quot; directory.
then run &quot;pcsx2-r2186_VC10.exe&quot;.
Note : Configuration Automatically Opens
If Not Then Apply Following Step

Step No : 02
1.Select &quot;Config&quot;
2.Select &quot;Configure&quot;

Step No : 03 

1.Click &quot;Set Bios Directory&quot;
2.Select the bios folder(provided besides iso)
3.Click &quot;Set Plugins Directory&quot;
4.Select the Plugins folder besides the iso
5.Goto &quot;Cdvdrom&quot;
6.Select &quot;Linuz Iso CDVD 0.8.0&quot;
7.make all the configurations as shown in &quot;config.jpeg&quot;
8.Select Final &quot;OK&quot; 

Step No:04
1.&quot;Return to Emulator&quot;
2.Select &quot;Run&quot; 
3.Select &quot;Execute&quot; 
4. select &quot;god of war.iso&quot;

all done!enjoy

if confused open the page &quot;how-to-play-playstation-2-ps2-games-on-pc&quot; but make configurations as &quot;config.jpeg&quot; only!

note:for increasing fps,goto config&gt;graphics and choose 'native'.
